<br />
<br />SMB3:  Some sounds pitches are way off.  Mario's jump is a lot lower, etc.
<br />
<br />Kirby:  The DPCM channels are overdriven and whenever they are active, the other channels are quiet.
<br />
<br />Overall, it seems to be crap.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_sad.gif" alt=":(" title="Sad" />
